class="user-agreement" id="eula-content">\r\n                                <p>C\xe1\xba\xa3m \xc6\xa1n b\xe1\xba\xa1n \xc4\x91\xc3\xa3 ch\xe1\xbb\x8dn tr\xc3\xacnh duy\xe1\xbb\x87t C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c. T\xe1\xbb\xabng \xc4\x91\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\xa3c bi\xe1\xba\xbft \xc4\x91\xe1\xba\xbfn v\xe1\xbb\x9bi t\xc3\xaan g\xe1\xbb\x8di \xe2\x80\x9cC\xe1\xbb\x9d R\xc3\xb4m+\xe2\x80\x9d, tr\xc3\xacnh duy\xe1\xbb\x87t C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c l\xc3\xa0 s\xe1\xba\xa3n ph\xe1\xba\xa9m c\xe1\xbb\xa7a C\xc3\xb4ng ty TNHH C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c, \xc4\x91\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\xa3c x\xc3\xa2y d\xe1\xbb\xb1ng t\xe1\xba\xa1i Vi\xe1\xbb\x87t Nam d\xe1\xbb\xb1a tr\xc3\xaan n\xe1\xbb\x81n t\xe1\xba\xa3ng m\xc3\xa3 ngu\xe1\xbb\x93n m\xe1\xbb\x9f Chromium (Tr\xc3\xacnh duy\xe1\xbb\x87t web C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c sau \xc4\x91\xc3\xa2y \xc4\x91\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\xa3c g\xe1\xbb\x8di t\xe1\xba\xaft l\xc3\xa0 "C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c"). C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c cung c\xe1\xba\xa5p cho b\xe1\xba\xa1n c\xc3\xa1c s\xe1\xba\xa3n ph\xe1\xba\xa9m, ph\xe1\xba\xa7n m\xe1\xbb\x81m, d\xe1\xbb\x8bch v\xe1\xbb\xa5 (g\xe1\xbb\x8di chung l\xc3\xa0 <strong>"D\xe1\xbb\x8bch v\xe1\xbb\xa5"</strong>) v\xe1\xbb\x9bi \xc4\x91i\xe1\xbb\x81u ki\xe1\xbb\x87n b\xe1\xba\xa1n ph\xe1\xba\xa3i \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x93ng \xc3\xbd v\xc3\xa0 tu\xc3\xa2n th\xe1\xbb\xa7 c\xc3\xa1c \xc4\x91i\xe1\xbb\x81u kho\xe1\xba\xa3n sau \xc4\x91\xc3\xa2y c\xe1\xbb\xa7a \xc4\x90i\xe1\xbb\x81u kho\xe1\xba\xa3n S\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng (<strong>"\xc4\x90i\xe1\xbb\x81u kho\xe1\xba\xa3n S\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng"</strong>)</p>\r\n                                <h4>1. QUY \xc4\x90\xe1\xbb\x8aNH CHUNG</h4>\r\n                                <p>\xc4\x90i\xe1\xbb\x81u kho\xe1\xba\xa3n S\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng quy \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x8bnh c\xc3\xa1c \xc4\x91i\xe1\xbb\x81u kho\xe1\xba\xa3n r\xc3\xa0ng bu\xe1\xbb\x99c b\xe1\xba\xa1n khi s\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng D\xe1\xbb\x8bch v\xe1\xbb\xa5 c\xe1\xbb\xa7a C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c. Thu\xe1\xba\xadt ng\xe1\xbb\xaf "B\xe1\xba\xa1n" v\xc3\xa0/ho\xe1\xba\xb7c "Ng\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\x9di s\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng" sau \xc4\x91\xc3\xa2y \xc4\x91\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\xa3c g\xe1\xbb\x8di chung \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x83 ch\xe1\xbb\x89 t\xe1\xbb\x9bi nh\xe1\xbb\xafng ng\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\x9di s\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng D\xe1\xbb\x8bch v\xe1\xbb\xa5 c\xe1\xbb\xa7a C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c. Vui l\xc3\xb2ng nghi\xc3\xaan c\xe1\xbb\xa9u k\xe1\xbb\xb9 v\xc3\xa0 l\xc6\xb0u l\xe1\xba\xa1i m\xe1\xbb\x99t b\xe1\xba\xa3n \xc4\x90i\xe1\xbb\x81u kho\xe1\xba\xa3n S\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng n\xc3\xa0y.</p>\r\n                                <p>B\xe1\xba\xb1ng vi\xe1\xbb\x87c t\xe1\xba\xa3i ph\xe1\xba\xa7n m\xe1\xbb\x81m v\xc3\xa0 s\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng D\xe1\xbb\x8bch v\xe1\xbb\xa5 c\xe1\xbb\xa7a ch\xc3\xbang t\xc3\xb4i, B\xe1\xba\xa1n \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x93ng \xc3\xbd b\xe1\xbb\x8b r\xc3\xa0ng bu\xe1\xbb\x99c v\xe1\xbb\x9bi \xc4\x90i\xe1\xbb\x81u kho\xe1\xba\xa3n S\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng n\xc3\xa0y. N\xe1\xba\xbfu B\xe1\xba\xa1n kh\xc3\xb4ng \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x93ng \xc3\xbd b\xe1\xbb\x8b r\xc3\xa0ng bu\xe1\xbb\x99c v\xe1\xbb\x9bi \xc4\x90i\xe1\xbb\x81u kho\xe1\xba\xa3n S\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng n\xc3\xa0y, B\xe1\xba\xa1n n\xc3\xaan ch\xe1\xba\xa5m d\xe1\xbb\xa9t ngay l\xe1\xba\xadp t\xe1\xbb\xa9c vi\xe1\xbb\x87c s\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng D\xe1\xbb\x8bch v\xe1\xbb\xa5 c\xe1\xbb\xa7a C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c.</p>\r\n                                <p>B\xe1\xba\xa1n x\xc3\xa1c nh\xe1\xba\xadn v\xc3\xa0 \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x93ng \xc3\xbd r\xe1\xba\xb1ng gi\xe1\xbb\xafa B\xe1\xba\xa1n v\xc3\xa0 C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c kh\xc3\xb4ng c\xc3\xb3 b\xe1\xba\xa5t k\xe1\xbb\xb3 m\xe1\xbb\x99t quan h\xe1\xbb\x87 li\xc3\xaan doanh, \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x91i t\xc3\xa1c, quan h\xe1\xbb\x87 lao \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x99ng, ho\xe1\xba\xb7c quan h\xe1\xbb\x87 \xc4\x91\xe1\xba\xa1i l\xc3\xbd n\xc3\xa0o xu\xe1\xba\xa5t ph\xc3\xa1t t\xe1\xbb\xab \xc4\x90i\xe1\xbb\x81u kho\xe1\xba\xa3n S\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng n\xc3\xa0y ho\xe1\xba\xb7c do vi\xe1\xbb\x87c B\xe1\xba\xa1n s\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng D\xe1\xbb\x8bch v\xe1\xbb\xa5 c\xe1\xbb\xa7a C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c. b\xc3\xad m\xe1\xba\xadt kh\xc3\xa1c \xc4\x91\xc3\xa3 \xc4\x91\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\xa3c ph\xc3\xa1p lu\xe1\xba\xadt quy \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x8bnh;</li>\r\n                                    <li>\xc4\x90\xc6\xb0a c\xc3\xa1c th\xc3\xb4ng tin xuy\xc3\xaan t\xe1\xba\xa1c, vu kh\xe1\xbb\x91ng, x\xc3\xbac ph\xe1\xba\xa1m uy t\xc3\xadn c\xe1\xbb\xa7a t\xe1\xbb\x95 ch\xe1\xbb\xa9c; danh d\xe1\xbb\xb1, nh\xc3\xa2n ph\xe1\xba\xa9m c\xe1\xbb\xa7a c\xc3\xb4ng d\xc3\xa2n;</li>\r\n                                    <li>L\xe1\xbb\xa3i d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng Internet \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x83 qu\xe1\xba\xa3ng c\xc3\xa1o, tuy\xc3\xaan truy\xe1\xbb\x81n, mua b\xc3\xa1n h\xc3\xa0ng ho\xc3\xa1, d\xe1\xbb\x8bch v\xe1\xbb\xa5 thu\xe1\xbb\x99c danh m\xe1\xbb\xa5c c\xe1\xba\xa5m theo quy \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x8bnh c\xe1\xbb\xa7a ph\xc3\xa1p lu\xe1\xba\xadt;</li>\r\n                                    <li>X\xc3\xa2m ph\xe1\xba\xa1m quy\xe1\xbb\x81n s\xe1\xbb\x9f h\xe1\xbb\xafu tr\xc3\xad tu\xe1\xbb\x87;</li>\r\n                                    <li>S\xe1\xba\xa3n xu\xe1\xba\xa5t, l\xc6\xb0u h\xc3\xa0nh s\xe1\xba\xa3n ph\xe1\xba\xa9m c\xc3\xb4ng ngh\xe1\xbb\x87 th\xc3\xb4ng tin tr\xc3\xa1i ph\xc3\xa1p lu\xe1\xba\xadt;</li>\r\n                                    <li>T\xe1\xba\xa1o \xc4\x91\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\x9dng d\xe1\xba\xabn tr\xc3\xa1i ph\xc3\xa9p \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x91i v\xe1\xbb\x9bi t\xc3\xaan mi\xe1\xbb\x81n c\xe1\xbb\xa7a t\xe1\xbb\x95 ch\xe1\xbb\xa9c, c\xc3\xa1 nh\xc3\xa2n s\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng h\xe1\xbb\xa3p ph\xc3\xa1p t\xc3\xaan mi\xe1\xbb\x81n \xc4\x91\xc3\xb3;</li>\r\n                                    <li>G\xc3\xa2y r\xe1\xbb\x91i, ph\xc3\xa1 ho\xe1\xba\xa1i h\xe1\xbb\x87 th\xe1\xbb\x91ng thi\xe1\xba\xbft b\xe1\xbb\x8b v\xc3\xa0 c\xe1\xba\xa3n tr\xe1\xbb\x9f tr\xc3\xa1i ph\xc3\xa1p lu\xe1\xba\xadt vi\xe1\xbb\x87c qu\xe1\xba\xa3n l\xc3\xbd, cung c\xe1\xba\xa5p, s\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng c\xc3\xa1c d\xe1\xbb\x8bch v\xe1\xbb\xa5 Internet v\xc3\xa0 th\xc3\xb4ng tin \xc4\x91i\xe1\xbb\x87n t\xe1\xbb\xad tr\xc3\xaan Internet;</li>\r\n                                    <li>\xc4\x90\xc3\xa1nh c\xe1\xba\xafp v\xc3\xa0 s\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng tr\xc3\xa1i ph\xc3\xa9p m\xe1\xba\xadt kh\xe1\xba\xa9u, kho\xc3\xa1 m\xe1\xba\xadt m\xc3\xa3 v\xc3\xa0 th\xc3\xb4ng tin ri\xc3\xaang c\xe1\xbb\xa7a c\xc3\xa1c t\xe1\xbb\x95 ch\xe1\xbb\xa9c, c\xc3\xa1 nh\xc3\xa2n tr\xc3\xaan Internet;</li>\r\n                                    <li>T\xe1\xba\xa1o ra v\xc3\xa0 c\xc3\xa0i \xc4\x91\xe1\xba\xb7t c\xc3\xa1c ch\xc6\xb0\xc6\xa1ng tr\xc3\xacnh virus m\xc3\xa1y t\xc3\xadnh, ph\xe1\xba\xa7n m\xe1\xbb\x81m g\xc3\xa2y h\xe1\xba\xa1i \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x83 th\xe1\xbb\xb1c hi\xe1\xbb\x87n m\xe1\xbb\x99t trong nh\xe1\xbb\xafng h\xc3\xa0nh vi tr\xc3\xa1i ph\xc3\xa1p lu\xe1\xba\xadt v\xe1\xbb\x81 c\xc3\xb4ng ngh\xe1\xbb\x87 th\xc3\xb4ng tin.</li>\r\n                                </ul>\r\n                                <br>\r\n                                <p><strong>4.2. C\xc3\xa1c h\xc3\xa0nh vi sau \xc4\x91\xc3\xa2y b\xe1\xbb\x8b coi l\xc3\xa0 l\xe1\xba\xa1m d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c v\xc3\xa0 b\xe1\xbb\x8b nghi\xc3\xaam c\xe1\xba\xa5m:</strong></p>\r\n                                <ul>\r\n                                    <li>Th\xc3\xb4ng b\xc3\xa1o v\xe1\xbb\x81 tr\xc3\xacnh duy\xe1\xbb\x87t C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c d\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\x9bi t\xc3\xaan g\xe1\xbb\x8di Chrome ho\xe1\xba\xb7c b\xe1\xba\xa5t k\xe1\xbb\xb3 t\xc3\xaan g\xe1\xbb\x8di n\xc3\xa0o kh\xc3\xa1c kh\xc3\xb4ng li\xc3\xaan quan \xc4\x91\xe1\xba\xbfn t\xc3\xaan th\xe1\xba\xadt c\xe1\xbb\xa7a C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c;</li>\r\n                                    <li>Thanh to\xc3\xa1n cho b\xe1\xba\xa5t k\xe1\xbb\xb3 b\xc3\xaan th\xe1\xbb\xa9 ba n\xc3\xa0o kh\xc3\xa1c trong m\xe1\xbb\x99t ch\xc6\xb0\xc6\xa1ng tr\xc3\xacnh h\xe1\xbb\xa3p t\xc3\xa1c c\xc3\xa1c kho\xe1\xba\xa3n doanh thu qu\xe1\xba\xa3ng c\xc3\xa1o c\xc3\xb3 \xc4\x91\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\xa3c t\xe1\xbb\xab c\xc3\xa1c l\xe1\xba\xa7n nh\xe1\xba\xa5p chu\xe1\xbb\x99t (clicks) c\xe1\xbb\xa7a ng\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\x9di s\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng tr\xc3\xacnh duy\xe1\xbb\x87t C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c, nh\xc6\xb0ng kh\xc3\xb4ng cho ph\xc3\xa9p C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c tham gia v\xc3\xa0o ch\xc6\xb0\xc6\xa1ng tr\xc3\xacnh h\xe1\xbb\xa3p t\xc3\xa1c \xc4\x91\xc3\xb3;</li>\r\n                                    <li>Kh\xc3\xb3a tr\xc3\xacnh duy\xe1\xbb\x87t C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c ho\xe1\xba\xb7c th\xc3\xb4ng b\xc3\xa1o sai s\xe1\xbb\xb1 th\xe1\xba\xadt r\xe1\xba\xb1ng tr\xc3\xacnh duy\xe1\xbb\x87t C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c kh\xc3\xb4ng \xc4\x91\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\xa3c h\xe1\xbb\x97 tr\xe1\xbb\xa3;</li>\r\n                                    <li>Ng\xc4\x83n ch\xc4\x83n vi\xe1\xbb\x87c t\xe1\xba\xa3i tr\xc3\xacnh duy\xe1\xbb\x87t C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c.</li>\r\n                                </ul>\r\n                                <p>B\xe1\xba\xa5t k\xe1\xbb\xb3 ng\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\x9di (ho\xe1\xba\xb7c c\xc3\xb4ng ty) n\xc3\xa0o th\xe1\xbb\xb1c hi\xe1\xbb\x87n m\xe1\xbb\x99t trong c\xc3\xa1c h\xc3\xa0nh vi \xc4\x91\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\xa3c n\xc3\xaau t\xe1\xba\xa1i m\xe1\xbb\xa5c 4.2 th\xc3\xac trong v\xc3\xb2ng 10 ng\xc3\xa0y l\xc3\xa0m vi\xe1\xbb\x87c sau m\xe1\xbb\x97i th\xc3\xa1ng, s\xe1\xba\xbd ph\xe1\xba\xa3i thanh to\xc3\xa1n cho C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c m\xe1\xbb\x99t ph\xe1\xba\xa7n gi\xc3\xa1 tr\xe1\xbb\x8b doanh thu qu\xe1\xba\xa3ng c\xc3\xa1o nh\xe1\xba\xadn \xc4\x91\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\xa3c t\xe1\xbb\xab c\xc3\xa1c l\xe1\xba\xa7n nh\xe1\xba\xa5p chu\xe1\xbb\x99t (clicks) c\xe1\xbb\xa7a ng\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\x9di s\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng tr\xc3\xacnh duy\xe1\xbb\x87t C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c, v\xe1\xbb\x9bi m\xe1\xbb\xa9c t\xc6\xb0\xc6\xa1ng \xc4\x91\xc6\xb0\xc6\xa1ng l\xc3\xa0 1000 VN\xc4\x90 (m\xe1\xbb\x99t ngh\xc3\xacn \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x93ng Vi\xe1\xbb\x87t nam)/ 01 click. N\xe1\xba\xbfu ng\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\x9di (ho\xe1\xba\xb7c c\xc3\xb4ng ty) \xc4\x91\xc3\xb3 vi ph\xe1\xba\xa1m th\xe1\xbb\x9di h\xe1\xba\xa1n thanh to\xc3\xa1n n\xc3\xaau tr\xc3\xaan, s\xe1\xba\xbd ph\xe1\xba\xa3i ch\xe1\xbb\x8bu ph\xe1\xba\xa1t 1% gi\xc3\xa1 tr\xe1\xbb\x8b cho m\xe1\xbb\x97i ng\xc3\xa0y thanh to\xc3\xa1n ch\xe1\xba\xadm. </p>\r\n                                <h4>5. QUY \xc4\x90\xe1\xbb\x8aNH S\xe1\xbb\xac D\xe1\xbb\xa4NG D\xe1\xbb\x8aCH V\xe1\xbb\xa4</h4>\r\n                                <p>Khi s\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng D\xe1\xbb\x8bch v\xe1\xbb\xa5 c\xe1\xbb\xa7a C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c, B\xe1\xba\xa1n b\xe1\xbb\x8b r\xc3\xa0ng bu\xe1\xbb\x99c ch\xe1\xba\xa5p thu\xe1\xba\xadn v\xc3\xa0 tu\xc3\xa2n th\xe1\xbb\xa7 c\xc3\xa1c \xc4\x91i\xe1\xbb\x81u ki\xe1\xbb\x87n quy \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x8bnh d\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\x9bi \xc4\x91\xc3\xa2y:</p>\r\n                                <ol style="list-style-type: lower-roman;">\r\n                                    <li>C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c c\xe1\xba\xa5p cho b\xe1\xba\xa1n s\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng mi\xe1\xbb\x85n ph\xc3\xad, kh\xc3\xb4ng t\xc3\xadnh ph\xc3\xad b\xe1\xba\xa3n quy\xe1\xbb\x81n, kh\xc3\xb4ng th\xe1\xbb\x83 chuy\xe1\xbb\x83n nh\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\xa3ng v\xc3\xa0 kh\xc3\xb4ng \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x99c quy\xe1\xbb\x81n \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x83 s\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng ph\xe1\xba\xa7n m\xe1\xbb\x81m tr\xc3\xacnh duy\xe1\xbb\x87t web C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c v\xc3\xa0 D\xe1\xbb\x8bch v\xe1\xbb\xa5. B\xe1\xba\xa1n kh\xc3\xb4ng \xc4\x91\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\xa3c v\xc3\xa0 kh\xc3\xb4ng cho ph\xc3\xa9p b\xe1\xba\xa5t k\xe1\xbb\xb3 ai kh\xc3\xa1c sao ch\xc3\xa9p, t\xe1\xba\xa1o s\xe1\xba\xa3n ph\xe1\xba\xa9m ph\xc3\xa1i sinh, ho\xe1\xba\xb7c c\xe1\xbb\x91 g\xe1\xba\xafng tr\xc3\xadch xu\xe1\xba\xa5t m\xc3\xa3 ngu\xe1\xbb\x93n c\xe1\xbb\xa7a ph\xe1\xba\xa7n m\xe1\xbb\x81m tr\xc3\xacnh duy\xe1\xbb\x87t web C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c.</li>\r\n                                    <li>Ph\xe1\xba\xa7n m\xe1\xbb\x81m tr\xc3\xacnh duy\xe1\xbb\x87t web C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c m\xc3\xa0 b\xe1\xba\xa1n s\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng c\xc3\xb3 th\xe1\xbb\x83 \xc4\x91\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\xa3c t\xe1\xbb\xb1 \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x99ng t\xe1\xba\xa3i xu\xe1\xbb\x91ng v\xc3\xa0 c\xc3\xa0i \xc4\x91\xe1\xba\xb7t th\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\x9dng xuy\xc3\xaan c\xc3\xa1c b\xe1\xba\xa3n c\xe1\xba\xadp nh\xe1\xba\xadt \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x83 s\xe1\xbb\xada ch\xe1\xbb\xafa, c\xe1\xba\xa3i ti\xe1\xba\xbfn, n\xc3\xa2ng cao v\xc3\xa0 ph\xc3\xa1t tri\xe1\xbb\x83n t\xe1\xbb\x91t h\xc6\xa1n c\xc3\xa1c D\xe1\xbb\x8bch v\xe1\xbb\xa5 c\xe1\xbb\xa7a C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c. Trong qu\xc3\xa1 tr\xc3\xacnh c\xe1\xba\xadp nh\xe1\xba\xadt, tr\xc3\xacnh duy\xe1\xbb\x87t C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c c\xc3\xb3 th\xe1\xbb\x83 ph\xc3\xa2n ph\xe1\xbb\x91i c\xc3\xa1c b\xe1\xba\xa3n c\xe1\xba\xadp nh\xe1\xba\xadt theo c\xc6\xa1 ch\xe1\xba\xbf peer to peer. B\xe1\xba\xa1n ch\xe1\xba\xa5p thu\xe1\xba\xadn v\xc3\xa0 cho ph\xc3\xa9p C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c s\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng c\xc6\xa1 ch\xe1\xba\xbf c\xe1\xba\xadp nh\xe1\xba\xadt tr\xc3\xacnh duy\xe1\xbb\x87t web nh\xc6\xb0 v\xe1\xba\xady trong qu\xc3\xa1 tr\xc3\xacnh s\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng D\xe1\xbb\x8bch v\xe1\xbb\xa5.</li>\r\n                                    <li>B\xe1\xba\xa1n \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x93ng \xc3\xbd v\xc3\xa0 c\xc3\xb4ng nh\xe1\xba\xadn r\xe1\xba\xb1ng c\xc3\xa1c N\xe1\xbb\x99i dung thu\xe1\xbb\x99c tr\xc3\xa1ch nhi\xe1\xbb\x87m c\xc3\xa1 nh\xc3\xa2n c\xe1\xbb\xa7a ng\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\x9di ch\xe1\xbb\xa7 s\xe1\xbb\x9f h\xe1\xbb\xafu N\xe1\xbb\x99i dung \xc4\x91\xc3\xb3. C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c \xc4\x91\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\xa3c quy\xe1\xbb\x81n nh\xc6\xb0ng kh\xc3\xb4ng c\xc3\xb3 ngh\xc4\xa9a v\xe1\xbb\xa5 ki\xe1\xbb\x83m duy\xe1\xbb\x87t, s\xc3\xa0ng l\xe1\xbb\x8dc, t\xe1\xbb\xab ch\xe1\xbb\x91i, s\xe1\xbb\xada \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x95i ho\xe1\xba\xb7c thay \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x95i b\xe1\xba\xa5t k\xe1\xbb\xb3 N\xe1\xbb\x99i dung n\xc3\xa0o c\xc3\xb3 s\xe1\xba\xb5n tr\xc3\xaan c\xc3\xa1c D\xe1\xbb\x8bch v\xe1\xbb\xa5 c\xe1\xbb\xa7a C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c. B\xe1\xba\xa1n ph\xe1\xba\xa3i t\xe1\xbb\xb1 ch\xe1\xbb\x8bu r\xe1\xbb\xa7i ro khi s\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng D\xe1\xbb\x8bch v\xe1\xbb\xa5 c\xe1\xbb\xa7a C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c m\xe1\xba\xb7c d\xc3\xb9 khi cung c\xe1\xba\xa5p D\xe1\xbb\x8bch v\xe1\xbb\xa5, C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c v\xe1\xba\xabn s\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng c\xc3\xa1c c\xc3\xb4ng c\xe1\xbb\xa5 \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x83 s\xc3\xa0ng l\xe1\xbb\x8dc th\xc3\xb4ng tin c\xc3\xb3 n\xe1\xbb\x99i dung kh\xc3\xb4ng ph\xc3\xb9 h\xe1\xbb\xa3p, vi ph\xe1\xba\xa1m quy \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x8bnh c\xe1\xbb\xa7a ph\xc3\xa1p lu\xe1\xba\xadt Vi\xe1\xbb\x87t Nam.</li>\r\n                                    <li>B\xe1\xba\xa1n \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x93ng \xc3\xbd r\xe1\xba\xb1ng B\xe1\xba\xa1n ph\xe1\xba\xa3i ch\xe1\xbb\x8bu tr\xc3\xa1ch nhi\xe1\xbb\x87m cho c\xc3\xa1c h\xc3\xa0nh vi c\xe1\xbb\xa7a m\xc3\xacnh v\xc3\xa0 cho b\xe1\xba\xa5t k\xe1\xbb\xb3 N\xe1\xbb\x99i dung n\xc3\xa0o m\xc3\xa0 B\xe1\xba\xa1n c\xc3\xb3 \xc4\x91\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\xa3c, t\xe1\xba\xa1o ra, tr\xc6\xb0ng b\xc3\xa0y ho\xe1\xba\xb7c truy\xe1\xbb\x81n t\xe1\xba\xa3i khi s\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng D\xe1\xbb\x8bch v\xe1\xbb\xa5 c\xe1\xbb\xa7a ch\xc3\xbang t\xc3\xb4i c\xc5\xa9ng nh\xc6\xb0 c\xc3\xa1c h\xe1\xba\xadu qu\xe1\xba\xa3 n\xe1\xba\xbfu c\xc3\xb3 xu\xe1\xba\xa5t ph\xc3\xa1t t\xe1\xbb\xab h\xc3\xa0nh vi s\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng v\xc3\xa0 N\xe1\xbb\x99i dung c\xe1\xbb\xa7a b\xe1\xba\xa1n. B\xe1\xba\xa1n \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x93ng \xc3\xbd r\xe1\xba\xb1ng b\xe1\xba\xa1n ch\xe1\xbb\x89 s\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng D\xe1\xbb\x8bch v\xe1\xbb\xa5 c\xe1\xbb\xa7a ch\xc3\xbang t\xc3\xb4i cho c\xc3\xa1c m\xe1\xbb\xa5c \xc4\x91\xc3\xadch h\xe1\xbb\xa3p ph\xc3\xa1p, h\xe1\xbb\xa3p l\xe1\xbb\x87, v\xc3\xa0 ph\xc3\xb9 h\xe1\xbb\xa3p v\xe1\xbb\x9bi c\xc3\xa1c quy \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x8bnh c\xe1\xbb\xa7a \xc4\x90i\xe1\xbb\x81u kho\xe1\xba\xa3n S\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng v\xc3\xa0 Ch\xc3\xadnh s\xc3\xa1ch B\xe1\xba\xa3o m\xe1\xba\xadt c\xe1\xbb\xa7a C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c c\xc5\xa9ng nh\xc6\xb0 c\xc3\xa1c h\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\x9bng d\xe1\xba\xabn hay ch\xc3\xadnh s\xc3\xa1ch kh\xc3\xa1c m\xc3\xa0 ch\xc3\xbang t\xc3\xb4i \xc3\xa1p d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng.</li>\r\n                                    <li>B\xe1\xba\xa1n \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x93ng \xc3\xbd r\xe1\xba\xb1ng C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c s\xe1\xba\xbd kh\xc3\xb4ng ch\xe1\xbb\x8bu tr\xc3\xa1ch nhi\xe1\xbb\x87m \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x91i v\xe1\xbb\x9bi vi\xe1\xbb\x87c b\xe1\xba\xa5t k\xe1\xbb\xb3 N\xe1\xbb\x99i dung n\xc3\xa0o c\xe1\xbb\xa7a B\xe1\xba\xa1n b\xe1\xbb\x8b x\xc3\xb3a ho\xe1\xba\xb7c kh\xc3\xb4ng l\xc6\xb0u tr\xe1\xbb\xaf \xc4\x91\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\xa3c trong qu\xc3\xa1 tr\xc3\xacnh ch\xc3\xbang t\xc3\xb4i duy tr\xc3\xac v\xc3\xa0 cung c\xe1\xba\xa5p c\xc3\xa1c D\xe1\xbb\x8bch v\xe1\xbb\xa5.</li>\r\n                                    <li>B\xe1\xba\xa1n \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x93ng \xc3\xbd r\xe1\xba\xb1ng B\xe1\xba\xa1n s\xe1\xba\xbd kh\xc3\xb4ng kinh doanh, khai th\xc3\xa1c, s\xe1\xba\xa3n xu\xe1\xba\xa5t l\xe1\xba\xa1i, sao ch\xc3\xa9p, s\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng c\xc3\xa1c D\xe1\xbb\x8bch v\xe1\xbb\xa5 c\xe1\xbb\xa7a C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c v\xc3\xac m\xe1\xbb\xa5c \xc4\x91\xc3\xadch th\xc6\xb0\xc6\xa1ng m\xe1\xba\xa1i tr\xe1\xbb\xab khi c\xc3\xb3 s\xe1\xbb\xb1 \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x93ng \xc3\xbd b\xe1\xba\xb1ng v\xc4\x83n b\xe1\xba\xa3n c\xe1\xbb\xa7a C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c.</li>\r\n                                    <li>B\xe1\xba\xa1n c\xc3\xb4ng nh\xe1\xba\xadn r\xe1\xba\xb1ng C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c cung c\xe1\xba\xa5p m\xe1\xbb\x99t s\xe1\xbb\x91 D\xe1\xbb\x8bch v\xe1\xbb\xa5 c\xc3\xb3 n\xe1\xbb\x99i dung qu\xe1\xba\xa3ng c\xc3\xa1o v\xc3\xa0 tr\xc6\xb0ng b\xc3\xa0y c\xc3\xa1c qu\xe1\xba\xa3ng c\xc3\xa1o v\xc3\xa0 khuy\xe1\xba\xbfn m\xc3\xa3i. B\xe1\xba\xa1n \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x93ng \xc3\xbd r\xe1\xba\xb1ng C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c c\xc3\xb3 th\xe1\xbb\x83 \xc4\x91\xe1\xba\xb7t th\xc3\xb4ng tin qu\xe1\xba\xa3ng c\xc3\xa1o v\xc3\xa0 khuy\xe1\xba\xbfn m\xc3\xa3i nh\xc6\xb0 v\xe1\xba\xady t\xe1\xba\xa1i c\xc3\xa1c D\xe1\xbb\x8bch v\xe1\xbb\xa5 v\xc3\xa0 C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c s\xe1\xba\xbd kh\xc3\xb4ng ch\xe1\xbb\x8bu b\xe1\xba\xa5t k\xe1\xbb\xb3 tr\xc3\xa1ch nhi\xe1\xbb\x87m n\xc3\xa0o \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x91i v\xe1\xbb\x9bi t\xe1\xbb\x95n th\xe1\xba\xa5t v\xc3\xa0 m\xe1\xba\xa5t m\xc3\xa1t m\xc3\xa0 B\xe1\xba\xa1n ph\xe1\xba\xa3i g\xc3\xa1nh ch\xe1\xbb\x8bu do s\xe1\xbb\xb1 xu\xe1\xba\xa5t hi\xe1\xbb\x87n c\xe1\xbb\xa7a c\xc3\xa1c d\xe1\xbb\x8bch v\xe1\xbb\xa5 qu\xe1\xba\xa3ng c\xc3\xa1o v\xc3\xa0 khuy\xe1\xba\xbfn m\xc3\xa3i ho\xe1\xba\xb7c B\xe1\xba\xa1n th\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\x9dng xuy\xc3\xaan ph\xe1\xba\xa3i nh\xe1\xba\xadn \xc4\x91\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\xa3c c\xc3\xa1c th\xc3\xb4ng tin qu\xe1\xba\xa3ng c\xc3\xa1o v\xc3\xa0 khuy\xe1\xba\xbfn m\xc3\xa3i nh\xc6\xb0 v\xe1\xba\xady khi s\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng D\xe1\xbb\x8bch v\xe1\xbb\xa5 c\xe1\xbb\xa7a C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c.</li>\r\n                                    <li>B\xe1\xba\xa1n c\xc3\xb4ng nh\xe1\xba\xadn r\xe1\xba\xb1ng C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c c\xc3\xb3 th\xe1\xbb\x83 li\xc3\xaan k\xe1\xba\xbft v\xe1\xbb\x9bi ho\xe1\xba\xb7c cung c\xe1\xba\xa5p \xc4\x91\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\x9dng link c\xe1\xbb\xa7a c\xc3\xa1c websites kh\xc3\xa1c v\xc3\xa0 B\xe1\xba\xa1n \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x93ng \xc3\xbd r\xe1\xba\xb1ng C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c kh\xc3\xb4ng ki\xe1\xbb\x83m so\xc3\xa1t v\xc3\xa0 ch\xe1\xbb\x8bu tr\xc3\xa1ch nhi\xe1\xbb\x87m \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x91i v\xe1\xbb\x9bi b\xe1\xba\xa5t k\xe1\xbb\xb3 N\xe1\xbb\x99i dung, qu\xe1\xba\xa3ng c\xc3\xa1o, d\xe1\xbb\x8bch v\xe1\xbb\xa5, s\xe1\xba\xa3n ph\xe1\xba\xa9m m\xc3\xa0 B\xe1\xba\xa1n c\xc3\xb3 \xc4\x91\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\xa3c hay bi\xe1\xba\xbft \xc4\x91\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\xa3c t\xe1\xbb\xab c\xc3\xa1c websites \xc4\x91\xc3\xb3. \xc4\x90\xe1\xbb\x93ng th\xe1\xbb\x9di B\xe1\xba\xa1n c\xc5\xa9ng x\xc3\xa1c nh\xe1\xba\xadn r\xe1\xba\xb1ng C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c s\xe1\xba\xbd kh\xc3\xb4ng ch\xe1\xbb\x8bu tr\xc3\xa1ch nhi\xe1\xbb\x87m \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x91i v\xe1\xbb\x9bi t\xe1\xbb\x95n th\xe1\xba\xa5t v\xc3\xa0 m\xe1\xba\xa5t m\xc3\xa1t m\xc3\xa0 B\xe1\xba\xa1n ph\xe1\xba\xa3i g\xc3\xa1nh ch\xe1\xbb\x8bu c\xc3\xb3 nguy\xc3\xaan nh\xc3\xa2n t\xe1\xbb\xab ho\xe1\xba\xb7c do vi\xe1\xbb\x87c B\xe1\xba\xa1n s\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng N\xe1\xbb\x99i dung, qu\xe1\xba\xa3ng c\xc3\xa1o, d\xe1\xbb\x8bch v\xe1\xbb\xa5, s\xe1\xba\xa3n ph\xe1\xba\xa9m t\xe1\xbb\xab c\xc3\xa1c website nh\xc6\xb0 v\xe1\xba\xady.</li>\r\n                                    <li>B\xe1\xba\xa1n \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x93ng \xc3\xbd r\xe1\xba\xb1ng B\xe1\xba\xa1n s\xe1\xba\xbd kh\xc3\xb4ng tham gia b\xe1\xba\xa5t k\xe1\xbb\xb3 ho\xe1\xba\xa1t \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x99ng hay th\xe1\xbb\xb1c hi\xe1\xbb\x87n b\xe1\xba\xa5t k\xe1\xbb\xb3 h\xc3\xa0nh vi n\xc3\xa0o c\xc3\xb3 th\xe1\xbb\x83 ho\xe1\xba\xb7c \xc4\x91e d\xe1\xbb\x8da l\xc3\xa0m gi\xc3\xa1n \xc4\x91o\xe1\xba\xa1n ho\xe1\xba\xb7c t\xe1\xba\xa1m ng\xe1\xbb\xabng D\xe1\xbb\x8bch v\xe1\xbb\xa5 c\xe1\xbb\xa7a C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c ho\xe1\xba\xb7c c\xc3\xa1c d\xe1\xbb\x8bch v\xe1\xbb\xa5 v\xc3\xa0 m\xe1\xba\xa1ng l\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\x9bi li\xc3\xaan k\xe1\xba\xbft v\xe1\xbb\x9bi c\xc3\xa1c D\xe1\xbb\x8bch v\xe1\xbb\xa5 c\xe1\xbb\xa7a C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c.</li>\r\n                                    <li>B\xe1\xba\xa1n \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x93ng \xc3\xbd r\xe1\xba\xb1ng C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c, v\xe1\xbb\x9bi to\xc3\xa0n quy\xe1\xbb\x81n quy\xe1\xba\xbft \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x8bnh c\xe1\xbb\xa7a m\xc3\xacnh, c\xc3\xb3 th\xe1\xbb\x83 d\xe1\xbb\xabng cung c\xe1\xba\xa5p c\xc3\xa1c D\xe1\xbb\x8bch v\xe1\xbb\xa5 cho b\xe1\xba\xa1n n\xe1\xba\xbfu C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c tin r\xe1\xba\xb1ng B\xe1\xba\xa1n \xc4\x91\xc3\xa3 vi ph\xe1\xba\xa1m ho\xe1\xba\xb7c th\xe1\xbb\xb1c hi\xe1\xbb\x87n kh\xc3\xb4ng \xc4\x91\xc3\xbang c\xc3\xa1c \xc4\x91i\xe1\xbb\x81u ki\xe1\xbb\x87n s\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng D\xe1\xbb\x8bch v\xe1\xbb\xa5 c\xe1\xbb\xa7a C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c.</li>\r\n                                    <li>B\xe1\xba\xa1n \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x93ng \xc3\xbd v\xc3\xa0 c\xc3\xb4ng nh\xe1\xba\xadn r\xe1\xba\xb1ng C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c c\xc3\xb3 to\xc3\xa0n quy\xe1\xbb\x81n quy\xe1\xba\xbft \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x8bnh v\xc3\xa0 v\xc3\xa0o b\xe1\xba\xa5t k\xe1\xbb\xb3 th\xe1\xbb\x9di \xc4\x91i\xe1\xbb\x83m n\xc3\xa0o ch\xe1\xba\xa5m d\xe1\xbb\xa9t vi\xe1\xbb\x87c cung c\xe1\xba\xa5p to\xc3\xa0n b\xe1\xbb\x99 ho\xe1\xba\xb7c m\xe1\xbb\x99t ph\xe1\xba\xa7n D\xe1\xbb\x8bch v\xe1\xbb\xa5, c\xc3\xb3 th\xe1\xbb\x83 ho\xe1\xba\xb7c kh\xc3\xb4ng c\xe1\xba\xa7n th\xc3\xb4ng b\xc3\xa1o. \xc4\x90\xe1\xbb\x93ng th\xe1\xbb\x9di, B\xe1\xba\xa1n \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x93ng \xc3\xbd r\xe1\xba\xb1ng C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c kh\xc3\xb4ng ch\xe1\xbb\x8bu tr\xc3\xa1ch nhi\xe1\xbb\x87m v\xe1\xbb\x9bi B\xe1\xba\xa1n ho\xe1\xba\xb7c v\xe1\xbb\x9bi b\xe1\xba\xa5t k\xe1\xbb\xb3 b\xc3\xaan th\xe1\xbb\xa9 ba n\xc3\xa0o do vi\xe1\xbb\x87c B\xe1\xba\xa1n b\xe1\xbb\x8b ch\xe1\xba\xa5m d\xe1\xbb\xa9t s\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng D\xe1\xbb\x8bch v\xe1\xbb\xa5.</li>\r\n                                    <li>B\xe1\xba\xa1n \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x93ng \xc3\xbd r\xe1\xba\xb1ng, C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c c\xc3\xb3 quy\xe1\xbb\x81n qu\xc3\xa9t d\xe1\xbb\xaf li\xe1\xbb\x87u t\xe1\xbb\xab b\xe1\xba\xa5t k\xe1\xbb\xb3 d\xe1\xbb\x8bch v\xe1\xbb\xa5 c\xc3\xb4ng c\xe1\xbb\x99ng n\xc3\xa0o m\xc3\xa0 b\xe1\xba\xa1n truy c\xe1\xba\xadp th\xc3\xb4ng qua tr\xc3\xacnh duy\xe1\xbb\x87t v\xc3\xa0 s\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng c\xc3\xa1c n\xe1\xbb\x99i dung mang t\xc3\xadnh c\xc3\xb4ng khai c\xe1\xbb\xa7a n\xc3\xb3 v\xc3\xa0o m\xe1\xbb\xa5c \xc4\x91\xc3\xadch n\xc3\xa2ng cao ch\xe1\xba\xa5t l\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\xa3ng duy\xe1\xbb\x87t web c\xe1\xbb\xa7a b\xe1\xba\xa1n, c\xc5\xa9ng nh\xc6\xb0 ch\xe1\xba\xa5t l\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\xa3ng c\xe1\xbb\xa7a c\xc3\xa1c d\xe1\xbb\x8bch v\xe1\xbb\xa5 m\xc3\xa0 b\xe1\xba\xa1n \xc4\x91ang s\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng v\xe1\xbb\x9bi C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c.</li>\r\n                                </ol>\r\n                                <br>\r\n                                <h4>6. GI\xe1\xbb\x9aI H\xe1\xba\xa0N TR\xc3\x81CH NHI\xe1\xbb\x86M</h4>\r\n                                <p>B\xe1\xba\xa1n x\xc3\xa1c nh\xe1\xba\xadn v\xc3\xa0 \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x93ng \xc3\xbd r\xe1\xba\xb1ng C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c ch\xe1\xbb\x89 s\xe1\xba\xb5n s\xc3\xa0ng cung c\xe1\xba\xa5p c\xc3\xa1c D\xe1\xbb\x8bch v\xe1\xbb\xa5 n\xe1\xba\xbfu B\xe1\xba\xa1n \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x93ng \xc3\xbd gi\xe1\xbb\x9bi h\xe1\xba\xa1n tr\xc3\xa1ch nhi\xe1\xbb\x87m c\xe1\xbb\xa7a ch\xc3\xbang t\xc3\xb4i \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x91i v\xe1\xbb\x9bi B\xe1\xba\xa1n v\xc3\xa0 c\xc3\xa1c b\xc3\xaan th\xe1\xbb\xa9 ba. B\xe1\xba\xa1n \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x93ng \xc3\xbd r\xe1\xba\xb1ng B\xe1\xba\xa1n ch\xe1\xbb\x8bu tr\xc3\xa1ch nhi\xe1\xbb\x87m b\xe1\xbb\x93i th\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\x9dng duy nh\xe1\xba\xa5t v\xc3\xa0 to\xc3\xa0n b\xe1\xbb\x99 \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x91i v\xe1\xbb\x9bi b\xe1\xba\xa5t k\xe1\xbb\xb3 khi\xe1\xba\xbfu n\xe1\xba\xa1i, t\xe1\xbb\x91 c\xc3\xa1o n\xc3\xa0o t\xe1\xbb\x9bi C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c li\xc3\xaan quan \xc4\x91\xe1\xba\xbfn b\xe1\xba\xa5t k\xe1\xbb\xb3 s\xe1\xbb\xb1 vi ph\xe1\xba\xa1m quy \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x8bnh s\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng n\xc3\xa0o do vi\xe1\xbb\x87c B\xe1\xba\xa1n ng\xe1\xbb\xabng s\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng D\xe1\xbb\x8bch v\xe1\xbb\xa5 c\xe1\xbb\xa7a C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c.</p>\r\n                                <p>B\xe1\xba\xa1n \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x93ng \xc3\xbd b\xe1\xba\xa3o v\xe1\xbb\x87, b\xe1\xbb\x93i th\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\x9dng v\xc3\xa0 gi\xe1\xbb\xaf cho C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c v\xc3\xa0 c\xc3\xa1c c\xc3\xb4ng ty li\xc3\xaan k\xe1\xba\xbft c\xe1\xbb\xa7a C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c kh\xc3\xb4ng b\xe1\xbb\x8b t\xe1\xbb\x95n h\xe1\xba\xa1i b\xe1\xbb\x9fi b\xe1\xba\xa5t k\xe1\xbb\xb3 khi\xe1\xba\xbfu n\xe1\xba\xa1i, khi\xe1\xba\xbfu ki\xe1\xbb\x87n, chi ph\xc3\xad, t\xe1\xbb\x95n th\xe1\xba\xa5t, thi\xe1\xbb\x87t h\xe1\xba\xa1i, ph\xc3\xa1n quy\xe1\xba\xbft c\xe1\xbb\xa7a t\xc3\xb2a \xc3\xa1n v\xc3\xa0 ph\xc3\xad t\xe1\xbb\x95n n\xc3\xa0o, bao g\xe1\xbb\x93m nh\xc6\xb0ng kh\xc3\xb4ng gi\xe1\xbb\x9bi h\xe1\xba\xa1n ph\xc3\xad lu\xe1\xba\xadt s\xc6\xb0, li\xc3\xaan quan \xc4\x91\xe1\xba\xbfn ho\xe1\xba\xb7c ph\xc3\xa1t sinh t\xe1\xbb\xab vi\xe1\xbb\x87c vi ph\xe1\xba\xa1m \xc4\x90i\xe1\xbb\x81u kho\xe1\xba\xa3n S\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng ho\xe1\xba\xb7c b\xe1\xba\xa5t k\xe1\xbb\xb3 s\xe1\xbb\xb1 s\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng c\xe1\xbb\xa7a B\xe1\xba\xa1n \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x91i v\xe1\xbb\x9bi c\xc3\xa1c D\xe1\xbb\x8bch v\xe1\xbb\xa5, ho\xe1\xba\xb7c b\xe1\xba\xa5t k\xe1\xbb\xb3 ng\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\x9di n\xc3\xa0o kh\xc3\xa1c s\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng D\xe1\xbb\x8bch v\xe1\xbb\xa5 th\xc3\xb4ng qua B\xe1\xba\xa1n ho\xe1\xba\xb7c s\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng m\xc3\xa1y t\xc3\xadnh c\xe1\xbb\xa7a B\xe1\xba\xa1n. C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c gi\xe1\xbb\xaf quy\xe1\xbb\x81n, b\xe1\xba\xb1ng chi ph\xc3\xad c\xe1\xbb\xa7a m\xc3\xacnh, \xc4\x91\xe1\xba\xa3m nh\xe1\xba\xadn ho\xc3\xa0n to\xc3\xa0n vi\xe1\xbb\x87c b\xe1\xba\xa3o v\xe1\xbb\x87 v\xc3\xa0 ki\xe1\xbb\x83m so\xc3\xa1t (nh\xc6\xb0ng kh\xc3\xb4ng c\xc3\xb3 tr\xc3\xa1ch nhi\xe1\xbb\x87m) \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x91i v\xe1\xbb\x9bi b\xe1\xba\xa5t k\xe1\xbb\xb3 v\xe1\xba\xa5n \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x81 n\xc3\xa0o ph\xc3\xa1t sinh nh\xc6\xb0 v\xe1\xba\xady t\xc3\xb9y thu\xe1\xbb\x99c v\xc3\xa0o s\xe1\xbb\xb1 b\xe1\xbb\x93i th\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\x9dng c\xe1\xbb\xa7a B\xe1\xba\xa1n.</p>\r\n                                <h4>7. B\xe1\xba\xa2O M\xe1\xba\xacT TH\xc3\x94NG TIN NG\xc6\xaf\xe1\xbb\x9cI D\xc3\x99NG</h4>\r\n                                <p>\xc4\x90\xe1\xbb\x83 hi\xe1\xbb\x83u r\xc3\xb5 c\xc6\xa1 ch\xe1\xba\xbf b\xe1\xba\xa3o m\xe1\xba\xadt th\xc3\xb4ng tin ng\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\x9di d\xc3\xb9ng, xin vui l\xc3\xb2ng tham kh\xe1\xba\xa3o Ch\xc3\xadnh s\xc3\xa1ch b\xe1\xba\xa3o m\xe1\xba\xadt c\xe1\xbb\xa7a C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c t\xe1\xba\xa1i website c\xe1\xbb\xa7a ch\xc3\xbang t\xc3\xb4i. Ch\xc3\xadnh s\xc3\xa1ch n\xc3\xa0y s\xe1\xba\xbd cung c\xe1\xba\xa5p cho c\xc3\xa1c b\xe1\xba\xa1n c\xc6\xa1 ch\xe1\xba\xbf thu t\xe1\xba\xadp, x\xe1\xbb\xad l\xc3\xbd v\xc3\xa0 b\xe1\xba\xa3o v\xe1\xbb\x87 th\xc3\xb4ng tin ng\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\x9di d\xc3\xb9ng. Khi b\xe1\xba\xa1n c\xc3\xa0i \xc4\x91\xe1\xba\xb7t v\xc3\xa0 s\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng tr\xc3\xacnh duy\xe1\xbb\x87t n\xc3\xa0y, b\xe1\xba\xa1n \xc4\x91\xc3\xa3 \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x93ng \xc3\xbd tu\xc3\xa2n theo Ch\xc3\xadnh s\xc3\xa1ch b\xe1\xba\xa3o m\xe1\xba\xadt c\xe1\xbb\xa7a C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c.</p>\r\n                                <h4>8. B\xe1\xba\xa2O V\xe1\xbb\x86 B\xe1\xba\xa2N QUY\xe1\xbb\x80N V\xc3\x80 QUY\xe1\xbb\x80N S\xe1\xbb\x9e H\xe1\xbb\xaeU TR\xc3\x8d TU\xe1\xbb\x86 KH\xc3\x81C</h4>\r\n                                <p>8.1. D\xe1\xbb\x8bch v\xe1\xbb\xa5 c\xe1\xbb\xa7a C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c v\xc3\xa0 t\xe1\xba\xa5t c\xe1\xba\xa3 c\xc3\xa1c ph\xe1\xba\xa7n m\xe1\xbb\x81m c\xe1\xba\xa7n thi\xe1\xba\xbft, y\xe1\xba\xbfu t\xe1\xbb\x91 c\xe1\xba\xa5u th\xc3\xa0nh c\xe1\xbb\xa7a D\xe1\xbb\x8bch v\xe1\xbb\xa5, bao g\xe1\xbb\x93m c\xe1\xba\xa3 c\xc3\xa1c quy\xe1\xbb\x81n s\xe1\xbb\x9f h\xe1\xbb\xafu tr\xc3\xad tu\xe1\xbb\x87 \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x91i v\xe1\xbb\x9bi D\xe1\xbb\x8bch v\xe1\xbb\xa5 c\xe1\xbb\xa7a C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c, v\xc3\xa0 t\xe1\xba\xa5t c\xe1\xba\xa3 c\xc3\xa1c ph\xe1\xba\xa7n m\xe1\xbb\x81m c\xe1\xba\xa7n thi\xe1\xba\xbft, y\xe1\xba\xbfu t\xe1\xbb\x91 c\xe1\xba\xa5u th\xc3\xa0nh c\xe1\xbb\xa7a D\xe1\xbb\x8bch v\xe1\xbb\xa5 ("S\xe1\xbb\x9f h\xe1\xbb\xafu Tr\xc3\xad tu\xe1\xbb\x87"), \xc4\x91\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\xa3c b\xe1\xba\xa3o v\xe1\xbb\x87 b\xe1\xbb\x9fi b\xe1\xba\xa3n quy\xe1\xbb\x81n, quy\xe1\xbb\x81n v\xe1\xbb\x81 th\xc6\xb0\xc6\xa1ng hi\xe1\xbb\x87u, nh\xc3\xa3n d\xe1\xbb\x8bch v\xe1\xbb\xa5, ho\xe1\xba\xb7c quy\xe1\xbb\x81n t\xc3\xa0i s\xe1\xba\xa3n kh\xc3\xa1c do C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c s\xe1\xbb\x9f h\xe1\xbb\xafu ho\xe1\xba\xb7c \xc4\x91\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\xa3c s\xe1\xbb\x9f h\xe1\xbb\xafu b\xe1\xbb\x9fi b\xc3\xaan th\xe1\xbb\xa9 ba n\xc3\xa0o m\xc3\xa0 \xc4\x91\xc3\xa3 c\xe1\xba\xa5p quy\xe1\xbb\x81n s\xe1\xbb\x9f h\xe1\xbb\xafu tr\xc3\xad tu\xe1\xbb\x87 cho C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c. B\xe1\xba\xa1n kh\xc3\xb4ng \xc4\x91\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\xa3c quy\xe1\xbb\x81n s\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng b\xe1\xba\xa5t k\xe1\xbb\xb3 t\xc3\xaan th\xc6\xb0\xc6\xa1ng m\xe1\xba\xa1i, nh\xc3\xa3n hi\xe1\xbb\x87u c\xe1\xbb\xa7a h\xc3\xa0ng h\xc3\xb3a v\xc3\xa0 d\xe1\xbb\x8bch v\xe1\xbb\xa5, bi\xe1\xbb\x83u t\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\xa3ng, t\xc3\xaan mi\xe1\xbb\x81n v\xc3\xa0 c\xc3\xa1c h\xc3\xacnh th\xe1\xbb\xa9c nh\xe1\xba\xadn di\xe1\xbb\x87n h\xc3\xa0ng h\xc3\xb3a, d\xe1\xbb\x8bch v\xe1\xbb\xa5 \xc4\x91\xe1\xba\xb7c tr\xc6\xb0ng n\xc3\xa0o kh\xc3\xa1c c\xe1\xbb\xa7a C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c v\xc3\xa0o m\xe1\xbb\xa5c \xc4\x91\xc3\xadch th\xc6\xb0\xc6\xa1ng m\xe1\xba\xa1i tr\xe1\xbb\xab khi B\xe1\xba\xa1n \xc4\x91\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\xa3c s\xe1\xbb\xb1 ch\xe1\xba\xa5p thu\xe1\xba\xadn b\xe1\xba\xb1ng v\xc4\x83n b\xe1\xba\xa3n c\xe1\xbb\xa7a C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c, ho\xe1\xba\xb7c vi\xe1\xbb\x87c s\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng c\xe1\xbb\xa7a B\xe1\xba\xa1n kh\xc3\xb4ng g\xc3\xa2y \xe1\xba\xa3nh h\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\x9fng, c\xe1\xba\xa3n tr\xe1\xbb\x9f, t\xc3\xa1c \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x99ng x\xe1\xba\xa5u t\xe1\xbb\x9bi vi\xe1\xbb\x87c ho\xe1\xba\xa1t \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x99ng b\xc3\xacnh th\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\x9dng c\xe1\xbb\xa7a C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c.<br>\r\n                                    S\xe1\xbb\xb1 bi\xc3\xaan t\xe1\xba\xadp (c\xc3\xb3 ngh\xc4\xa9a l\xc3\xa0 thu th\xe1\xba\xadp, s\xe1\xba\xafp x\xe1\xba\xbfp, v\xc3\xa0 t\xe1\xba\xadp h\xe1\xbb\xa3p) c\xe1\xbb\xa7a t\xe1\xba\xa5t c\xe1\xba\xa3 S\xe1\xbb\x9f h\xe1\xbb\xafu Tr\xc3\xad tu\xe1\xbb\x87 c\xe1\xbb\xa7a D\xe1\xbb\x8bch v\xe1\xbb\xa5 l\xc3\xa0 t\xc3\xa0i s\xe1\xba\xa3n \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x99c quy\xe1\xbb\x81n c\xe1\xbb\xa7a C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c v\xc3\xa0 \xc4\x91\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\xa3c b\xe1\xba\xa3o v\xe1\xbb\x87 b\xe1\xbb\x9fi ph\xc3\xa1p lu\xe1\xba\xadt Vi\xe1\xbb\x87t Nam v\xc3\xa0 c\xc3\xa1c c\xc3\xb4ng \xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\x9bc qu\xe1\xbb\x91c t\xe1\xba\xbf v\xe1\xbb\x81 b\xe1\xba\xa3n quy\xe1\xbb\x81n. S\xe1\xbb\x9f h\xe1\xbb\xafu tr\xc3\xad tu\xe1\xbb\x87 c\xe1\xbb\xa7a D\xe1\xbb\x8bch v\xe1\xbb\xa5 v\xc3\xa0 c\xc3\xa1c d\xe1\xbb\x8bch v\xe1\xbb\xa5 kh\xc3\xa1c m\xc3\xa0 C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c s\xe1\xbb\x9f h\xe1\xbb\xafu, v\xe1\xba\xadn h\xc3\xa0nh, ki\xe1\xbb\x83m so\xc3\xa1t, ho\xe1\xba\xb7c \xc4\x91\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\xa3c c\xe1\xba\xa5p ph\xc3\xa9p kh\xc3\xb4ng \xc4\x91\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\xa3c sao ch\xe1\xbb\xa5p, s\xe1\xba\xa3n xu\xe1\xba\xa5t l\xe1\xba\xa1i, t\xc3\xa1i b\xe1\xba\xa3n, t\xe1\xba\xa3i l\xc3\xaan, \xc4\x91\xc4\x83ng l\xc3\xaan, truy\xe1\xbb\x81n t\xe1\xba\xa3i, ho\xe1\xba\xb7c ph\xc3\xa2n ph\xe1\xbb\x91i d\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\x9bi b\xe1\xba\xa5t k\xe1\xbb\xb3 h\xc3\xacnh th\xe1\xbb\xa9c n\xc3\xa0o. Vi\xe1\xbb\x87c s\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng ho\xe1\xba\xb7c s\xe1\xbb\xada \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x95i quy\xe1\xbb\x81n s\xe1\xbb\x9f h\xe1\xbb\xafu tr\xc3\xad tu\xe1\xbb\x87 c\xe1\xbb\xa7a C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c d\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\x9bi b\xe1\xba\xa5t k\xe1\xbb\xb3 h\xc3\xacnh th\xe1\xbb\xa9c n\xc3\xa0o, bao g\xe1\xbb\x93m nh\xc6\xb0ng kh\xc3\xb4ng gi\xe1\xbb\x9bi h\xe1\xba\xa1n t\xe1\xbb\x9bi b\xe1\xba\xa5t k\xe1\xbb\xb3 website ho\xe1\xba\xb7c m\xc3\xb4i tr\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\x9dng \xc4\x91\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\xa3c k\xe1\xba\xbft n\xe1\xbb\x91i m\xc3\xa1y vi t\xc3\xadnh n\xc3\xa0o, m\xc3\xa0 kh\xc3\xb4ng \xc4\x91\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\xa3c s\xe1\xbb\xb1 ch\xe1\xba\xa5p thu\xe1\xba\xadn tr\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\x9bc b\xe1\xba\xb1ng v\xc4\x83n b\xe1\xba\xa3n l\xc3\xa0 vi ph\xe1\xba\xa1m b\xe1\xba\xa3n quy\xe1\xbb\x81n v\xc3\xa0 c\xc3\xa1c quy\xe1\xbb\x81n t\xc3\xa0i s\xe1\xba\xa3n kh\xc3\xa1c c\xe1\xbb\xa7a C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c v\xc3\xa0 b\xe1\xbb\x8b nghi\xc3\xaam c\xe1\xba\xa5m.</p>\r\n                                <p>8.2. Theo \xc4\x90i\xe1\xbb\x81u kho\xe1\xba\xa3n n\xc3\xa0y, C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c t\xc3\xb4n tr\xe1\xbb\x8dng v\xc3\xa0 kh\xc3\xb4ng t\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\x9bc \xc4\x91o\xe1\xba\xa1t quy\xe1\xbb\x81n s\xe1\xbb\x9f h\xe1\xbb\xafu ho\xe1\xba\xb7c c\xc3\xa1c quy\xe1\xbb\x81n kh\xc3\xa1c c\xe1\xbb\xa7a b\xe1\xba\xa1n \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x91i v\xe1\xbb\x9bi c\xc3\xa1c N\xe1\xbb\x99i dung b\xe1\xba\xa1n g\xe1\xbb\xadi, \xc4\x91\xc4\x83ng, chuy\xe1\xbb\x83n giao ho\xe1\xba\xb7c hi\xe1\xbb\x83n th\xe1\xbb\x8b tr\xc3\xaan tr\xc3\xacnh duy\xe1\xbb\x87t c\xe1\xbb\xa7a ch\xc3\xbang t\xc3\xb4i. B\xe1\xba\xa1n \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x93ng \xc3\xbd ch\xe1\xbb\x8bu tr\xc3\xa1ch nhi\xe1\xbb\x87m b\xe1\xba\xa3o v\xe1\xbb\x87 v\xc3\xa0 thi h\xc3\xa0nh c\xc3\xa1c quy\xe1\xbb\x81n \xc4\x91\xc3\xb3, v\xc3\xa0 C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c kh\xc3\xb4ng c\xc3\xb3 ngh\xc4\xa9a v\xe1\xbb\xa5 th\xe1\xbb\xb1c hi\xe1\xbb\x87n c\xc3\xb4ng vi\xe1\xbb\x87c \xc4\x91\xc3\xb3 nh\xc3\xa2n danh b\xe1\xba\xa1n tr\xe1\xbb\xab khi gi\xe1\xbb\xafa b\xe1\xba\xa1n v\xc3\xa0 C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c c\xc3\xb3 th\xe1\xbb\x8fa thu\xe1\xba\xadn ri\xc3\xaang b\xe1\xba\xb1ng v\xc4\x83n b\xe1\xba\xa3n v\xe1\xbb\x81 v\xe1\xba\xa5n \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x81 n\xc3\xa0y.</p>\r\n                                <p>8.3. Ch\xc3\xbang t\xc3\xb4i t\xc3\xb4n tr\xe1\xbb\x8dng quy\xe1\xbb\x81n s\xe1\xbb\x9f h\xe1\xbb\xafu tr\xc3\xad tu\xe1\xbb\x87 c\xe1\xbb\xa7a ng\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\x9di kh\xc3\xa1c v\xc3\xa0 y\xc3\xaau c\xe1\xba\xa7u Ng\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\x9di s\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng c\xe1\xbb\xa7a C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c c\xc5\xa9ng nh\xc6\xb0 v\xe1\xba\xady. B\xe1\xba\xa1n kh\xc3\xb4ng \xc4\x91\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\xa3c t\xe1\xba\xa3i l\xc3\xaan, g\xe1\xba\xafn v\xc3\xa0o, \xc4\x91\xc4\x83ng l\xc3\xaan, truy\xe1\xbb\x81n \xc4\x91i ho\xe1\xba\xb7c b\xe1\xba\xb1ng c\xc3\xa1ch kh\xc3\xa1c t\xe1\xba\xa1o s\xe1\xba\xb5n b\xe1\xba\xa5t k\xe1\xbb\xb3 y\xe1\xba\xbfu t\xe1\xbb\x91 c\xe1\xba\xa5u th\xc3\xa0nh n\xc3\xa0o g\xc3\xa2y \xe1\xba\xa3nh h\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\x9fng \xc4\x91\xe1\xba\xbfn b\xe1\xba\xa3n quy\xe1\xbb\x81n, th\xc6\xb0\xc6\xa1ng hi\xe1\xbb\x87u, b\xc3\xad m\xe1\xba\xadt th\xc6\xb0\xc6\xa1ng m\xe1\xba\xa1i ho\xe1\xba\xb7c quy\xe1\xbb\x81n t\xc3\xa0i s\xe1\xba\xa3n kh\xc3\xa1c c\xe1\xbb\xa7a b\xe1\xba\xa5t k\xe1\xbb\xb3 t\xe1\xbb\x95 ch\xe1\xbb\xa9c ho\xe1\xba\xb7c c\xc3\xa1 nh\xc3\xa2n n\xc3\xa0o. Ch\xc3\xbang t\xc3\xb4i c\xc3\xb3 quy\xe1\xbb\x81n ch\xe1\xba\xa5m d\xe1\xbb\xa9t \xc4\x91\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\x9dng truy c\xe1\xba\xadp v\xc3\xa0o D\xe1\xbb\x8bch v\xe1\xbb\xa5 c\xe1\xbb\xa7a C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c ho\xe1\xba\xb7c b\xe1\xba\xa5t k\xe1\xbb\xb3 d\xe1\xbb\x8bch v\xe1\xbb\xa5 n\xc3\xa0o do C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c cung c\xe1\xba\xa5p \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x91i v\xe1\xbb\x9bi ng\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\x9di b\xe1\xbb\x8b nghi ng\xe1\xbb\x9d x\xc3\xa2m ph\xe1\xba\xa1m.</p>\r\n                                <h4>9. \xc4\x90I\xe1\xbb\x80U KHO\xe1\xba\xa2N KH\xc3\x81C</h4>\r\n                                <p><strong>9.1. Lu\xe1\xba\xadt \xc4\x91i\xe1\xbb\x81u ch\xe1\xbb\x89nh</strong><br>\r\n                                    \xc4\x90i\xe1\xbb\x81u kho\xe1\xba\xa3n S\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng n\xc3\xa0y \xc4\x91\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\xa3c \xc4\x91i\xe1\xbb\x81u ch\xe1\xbb\x89nh b\xe1\xbb\x9fi v\xc3\xa0 gi\xe1\xba\xa3i th\xc3\xadch ph\xc3\xb9 h\xe1\xbb\xa3p v\xe1\xbb\x9bi ph\xc3\xa1p lu\xe1\xba\xadt Vi\xe1\xbb\x87t Nam. N\xe1\xba\xbfu b\xe1\xba\xa5t k\xe1\xbb\xb3 \xc4\x91i\xe1\xbb\x81u kho\xe1\xba\xa3n n\xc3\xa0o trong \xc4\x90i\xe1\xbb\x81u kho\xe1\xba\xa3n S\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng n\xc3\xa0y kh\xc3\xb4ng h\xe1\xbb\xa3p ph\xc3\xa1p, v\xc3\xb4 hi\xe1\xbb\x87u ho\xe1\xba\xb7c v\xc3\xac b\xe1\xba\xa5t k\xe1\xbb\xb3 l\xc3\xbd do n\xc3\xa0o kh\xc3\xb4ng th\xe1\xbb\x83 th\xe1\xbb\xb1c hi\xe1\xbb\x87n \xc4\x91\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\xa3c, th\xc3\xac \xc4\x91i\xe1\xbb\x81u kho\xe1\xba\xa3n \xc4\x91\xc3\xb3 s\xe1\xba\xbd \xc4\x91\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\xa3c xem l\xc3\xa0 t\xc3\xa1ch r\xe1\xbb\x9di kh\xe1\xbb\x8fi \xc4\x90i\xe1\xbb\x81u kho\xe1\xba\xa3n S\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng n\xc3\xa0y v\xc3\xa0 kh\xc3\xb4ng \xe1\xba\xa3nh h\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\x9fng \xc4\x91\xe1\xba\xbfn hi\xe1\xbb\x87u l\xe1\xbb\xb1c v\xc3\xa0 t\xc3\xadnh th\xe1\xbb\xb1c thi c\xe1\xbb\xa7a c\xc3\xa1c \xc4\x91i\xe1\xbb\x81u kho\xe1\xba\xa3n c\xc3\xb2n l\xe1\xba\xa1i c\xe1\xbb\xa7a \xc4\x90i\xe1\xbb\x81u kho\xe1\xba\xa3n S\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng n\xc3\xa0y.</p>\r\n                                <p><strong>9.2. Ch\xe1\xba\xa5m d\xe1\xbb\xa9t</strong><br>\r\n                                    \xc4\x90i\xe1\xbb\x81u kho\xe1\xba\xa3n S\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng n\xc3\xa0y c\xc3\xb3 hi\xe1\xbb\x87u l\xe1\xbb\xb1c cho \xc4\x91\xe1\xba\xbfn khi b\xe1\xbb\x8b ch\xe1\xba\xa5m d\xe1\xbb\xa9t b\xe1\xbb\x9fi B\xe1\xba\xa1n ho\xe1\xba\xb7c b\xe1\xbb\x9fi C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c theo c\xc3\xa1c tr\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\x9dng h\xe1\xbb\xa3p sau \xc4\x91\xc3\xa2y:</p>\r\n                                <ol style="list-style-type: lower-roman;">\r\n                                    <li>Ch\xe1\xba\xa5m d\xe1\xbb\xa9t b\xe1\xbb\x9fi B\xe1\xba\xa1n: B\xe1\xba\xa1n c\xc3\xb3 th\xe1\xbb\x83 ch\xe1\xba\xa5m d\xe1\xbb\xa9t \xc4\x90i\xe1\xbb\x81u kho\xe1\xba\xa3n S\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng n\xc3\xa0y b\xe1\xba\xb1ng c\xc3\xa1ch kh\xc3\xb4ng s\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng D\xe1\xbb\x8bch v\xe1\xbb\xa5 c\xe1\xbb\xa7a C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c n\xe1\xbb\xafa.</li>\r\n                                    <li>Ch\xe1\xba\xa5m d\xe1\xbb\xa9t b\xe1\xbb\x9fi C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c: \xc4\x90i\xe1\xbb\x81u kho\xe1\xba\xa3n S\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng n\xc3\xa0y ch\xe1\xba\xa5m d\xe1\xbb\xa9t ngay l\xe1\xba\xadp t\xe1\xbb\xa9c m\xc3\xa0 C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c kh\xc3\xb4ng c\xe1\xba\xa7n ph\xe1\xba\xa3i th\xc3\xb4ng b\xc3\xa1o tr\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\x9bc n\xe1\xba\xbfu (i) theo s\xe1\xbb\xb1 quy\xe1\xba\xbft \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x8bnh c\xe1\xbb\xa7a C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c, B\xe1\xba\xa1n kh\xc3\xb4ng tu\xc3\xa2n th\xe1\xbb\xa7 b\xe1\xba\xa5t k\xe1\xbb\xb3 \xc4\x91i\xe1\xbb\x81u kho\xe1\xba\xa3n n\xc3\xa0o c\xe1\xbb\xa7a \xc4\x90i\xe1\xbb\x81u kho\xe1\xba\xa3n S\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng n\xc3\xa0y ho\xe1\xba\xb7c (ii) Ph\xc3\xa1p lu\xe1\xba\xadt ho\xe1\xba\xb7c quy\xe1\xba\xbft \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x8bnh c\xe1\xbb\xa7a ch\xc3\xadnh ph\xe1\xbb\xa7, t\xc3\xb2a \xc3\xa1n, c\xc6\xa1 quan thi h\xc3\xa0nh \xc3\xa1n y\xc3\xaau c\xe1\xba\xa7u C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c ch\xe1\xba\xa5m d\xe1\xbb\xa9t \xc4\x90i\xe1\xbb\x81u kho\xe1\xba\xa3n S\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng.</li>\r\n                                </ol>\r\n                                <p>Khi ch\xe1\xba\xa5m d\xe1\xbb\xa9t \xc4\x90i\xe1\xbb\x81u kho\xe1\xba\xa3n S\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng n\xc3\xa0y, B\xe1\xba\xa1n ph\xe1\xba\xa3i h\xe1\xbb\xa7y b\xe1\xbb\x8f t\xe1\xba\xa5t c\xe1\xba\xa3 th\xc3\xb4ng tin, t\xc6\xb0 li\xe1\xbb\x87u nh\xe1\xba\xadn \xc4\x91\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\xa3c t\xe1\xbb\xab C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c v\xc3\xa0 c\xc3\xa1c website c\xe1\xbb\xa7a C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c, c\xc5\xa9ng nh\xc6\xb0 t\xe1\xba\xa5t c\xe1\xba\xa3 b\xe1\xba\xa3n sao c\xe1\xbb\xa7a th\xc3\xb4ng tin, t\xc6\xb0 li\xe1\xbb\x87u \xc4\x91\xc3\xb3, d\xc3\xb9 \xc4\x91\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\xa3c l\xe1\xba\xadp b\xe1\xbb\x9fi theo c\xc3\xa1c quy \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x8bnh c\xe1\xbb\xa7a \xc4\x90i\xe1\xbb\x81u kho\xe1\xba\xa3n S\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng n\xc3\xa0y ho\xe1\xba\xb7c c\xe1\xbb\xa7a c\xc3\xa1c quy \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x8bnh kh\xc3\xa1c.</p>\r\n                                <strong>9.3. Li\xc3\xaan h\xe1\xbb\x87</strong>\r\n                                <p>N\xe1\xba\xbfu B\xe1\xba\xa1n c\xc3\xb3 b\xe1\xba\xa5t k\xe1\xbb\xb3 c\xc3\xa2u h\xe1\xbb\x8fi n\xc3\xa0o v\xe1\xbb\x81 \xc4\x90i\xe1\xbb\x81u kho\xe1\xba\xa3n S\xe1\xbb\xad d\xe1\xbb\xa5ng n\xc3\xa0y, v\xe1\xbb\x81 ho\xe1\xba\xa1t \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x99ng c\xe1\xbb\xa7a website Coccoc.com, ho\xe1\xba\xb7c s\xe1\xbb\xb1 k\xe1\xba\xbft n\xe1\xbb\x91i c\xe1\xbb\xa7a B\xe1\xba\xa1n v\xe1\xbb\x9bi C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c, vui l\xc3\xb2ng li\xc3\xaan h\xe1\xbb\x87 v\xe1\xbb\x9bi ch\xc3\xbang t\xc3\xb4i qua email: <a href="mailto:info@Coccoc.com">info@Coccoc.com</a>. T\xe1\xba\xa5t c\xe1\xba\xa3 c\xc3\xa1c v\xe1\xba\xa5n \xc4\x91\xe1\xbb\x81 ho\xe1\xba\xb7c m\xc3\xa2u thu\xe1\xba\xabn s\xe1\xba\xbd \xc4\x91\xc6\xb0\xe1\xbb\xa3c gi\xe1\xba\xa3i quy\xe1\xba\xbft nhanh ch\xc3\xb3ng v\xc3\xa0 h\xe1\xbb\xa3p l\xc3\xbd.</p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div tri\xe1\xbb\x83n C\xe1\xbb\x91c C\xe1\xbb\x91c.</div>\r\n                <div class="cc-modal-download-bottom js-cc-download">\r\n                    <a href="#"
